{"tid":465832,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人搞錯左有教無類嘅意思","createTime":"2017-11-12T03:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T05:17:20.000Z","uid":23423,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c60dbb34033308e7589c2557136bca1e4e9eace3","tid":465832,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T03:38:21.000Z","msg":"《論語&middot;衛靈公》：&ldquo;子曰：&lsquo;有教無類。&rsquo;&rdquo;<br />\n孔子性格大家都知，十分剛烈，人若犯佢，佢係一定口誅筆伐。<br />\n佢唔係大愛撚，唔係墨家嘅兼愛，主張以直報怨，愛有等差，係先老吾老，先幼吾幼。<br />\n佢提出有教無類係因為當時學舍根本就唔準庶民報名出席，有教無類係話佢想學，就應該俾佢學。<br />\n<br />\n現時就被濫用為佢唔想學，老師都有責任逼佢學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  新聞出現啲垃圾學校垃圾學生自己都無心向學，結果學校唔理佢就屌學校唔識有教無類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cfce5a7beb9283c33592e2b48dcb31b88e73a1","tid":465832,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30b6e9b3f28c263202f86fb690c7e4be35e46f6","tid":465832,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669ba162db60eea2bf97c1a244cb3056eb545e03","tid":465832,"uid":69754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"正常點會用錯 <br />\n照字面解都解到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f55927790b95ab34afce464b4b2731b5f1b3160","tid":465832,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常點會用錯 <br />\n照字面解都解到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇下高連兩登嘅Post就知<br />\n有人話&rdquo;個班學生根本就唔想讀書 點解仲要浪費時間落佢地到&rdquo;<br />\n通常回覆就係&rdquo;有教無類啊 教畜&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7af5b04df01422eb7ee14fb127920af3b49dc42f","tid":465832,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12